<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 02:27:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列卫生当局怀疑两名老年妇女死于西尼罗河病毒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-health-authorities-suspect-two-elderly-women-died-of-west-nile-virus/00000190-410a-d768-adf8-4dba33220000</link><description>导致妇女死亡的佩塔提克瓦医院正在等待实验室结果以确认死因 ■ 自 5 月以来，已有 19 名以色列人被诊断出感染该病毒，这是一个相对较高的数字 ■ 卫生部表示，今年早些时候出现了感染，可能是因为气候改变</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 18:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-health-authorities-suspect-two-elderly-women-died-of-west-nile-virus/00000190-410a-d768-adf8-4dba33220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事，第 260 天：以色列国防军试图暗杀哈马斯官员；加沙人报告超过 40 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-260-idf-tries-to-assassinate-hamas-official-gazans-say-over-40-dead/00000190-40d1-d91c-abba-efd120ec0000</link><description>以色列国防军：试图在加沙城暗杀哈马斯高级官员；哈马斯：以色列两次袭击造成 42 人死亡 ■ 受伤的巴勒斯坦男子在约旦河西岸被捕后在以色列国防军车辆的引擎盖上被拍摄；以色列国防军：违反军队礼节的行为 ■ 60 岁的以色列人在约旦河西岸被巴勒斯坦人杀害 ■ 以色列国防军称其在黎巴嫩暗杀了哈马斯的主要特工 ■ 以下是战争 260 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 17:00:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-260-idf-tries-to-assassinate-hamas-official-gazans-say-over-40-dead/00000190-40d1-d91c-abba-efd120ec0000</guid></item><item><title>数万名以色列人抗议政府，要求人质协议；三人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israelis-set-to-protest-netanyahus-coalition-demand-hostage-deal-across-country/00000190-409f-da42-a1ba-7fffc1660000</link><description>以色列主要城市和全国各地都在发生抗议活动。一名获释人质表示，她感到自己被政府“背叛”，而一名人质的兄弟则向内塔尼亚胡讲话，指责他“将政治生存置于亲人生命之上”</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 16:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israelis-set-to-protest-netanyahus-coalition-demand-hostage-deal-across-country/00000190-409f-da42-a1ba-7fffc1660000</guid></item><item><title>视频显示受伤的巴勒斯坦人被绑在以色列国防军吉普车引擎盖上； 12 岁儿童在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军枪击身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-video-shows-wounded-palestinian-on-idf-jeep-hood-12-year-old-dies-by-idf-fire/00000190-4039-d429-abfc-797bb1b20000</link><description>以色列军方表示，这段视频违反了其命令和程序；巴勒斯坦青少年在约旦河西岸村庄的冲突中受伤几天后死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 15:31:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-video-shows-wounded-palestinian-on-idf-jeep-hood-12-year-old-dies-by-idf-fire/00000190-4039-d429-abfc-797bb1b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列试图暗杀加沙哈马斯高级指挥官；巴勒斯坦人报告超过 40 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-tries-to-assassinate-top-hamas-commander-in-gaza-palestinians-report-over-40-dead/00000190-401a-d5e8-a7f0-cd1f16fc0000</link><description>德国德新社报道称，哈马斯的目标官员是该组织行动部门负责人拉德·萨阿德，而以色列军方表示正在调查有关周五致命袭击的报道</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 14:49:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-tries-to-assassinate-top-hamas-commander-in-gaza-palestinians-report-over-40-dead/00000190-401a-d5e8-a7f0-cd1f16fc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子在约旦河西岸盖勒吉利亚被杀；国防部官员：可能是恐怖袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-killed-in-west-bank-city-of-qalqilya-intent-of-attack-still-under-inve/00000190-3ec9-d8cb-a19d-7fcb967b0000</link><description>一名 60 岁的以色列男子在 Qalqilya 被枪杀，随后伤重不治。视频显示，巴勒斯坦医疗队正在救治这名男子，该男子后来在以色列拘留期间死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 08:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-killed-in-west-bank-city-of-qalqilya-intent-of-attack-still-under-inve/00000190-3ec9-d8cb-a19d-7fcb967b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预备役军人在加沙南部拉法的战斗事故中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-live/25-gazans-reported-dead-in-rafah-strike-idf-first-probe-does-not-indicate-strike-there/00000190-3dea-d8cb-a19d-7debec640005</link><description>以色列各地数千人抗议政府和人质交易 ■ 以色列国防军试图在加沙城暗杀哈马斯官员；巴勒斯坦人报告超过 40 人死亡 ■ 60 岁的以色列人在约旦河西岸盖勒吉利耶被枪杀 ■ 以色列军队表示，他们在黎巴嫩深处的无人机袭击中暗杀了哈马斯的关键成员 ■ 反坦克导弹在以色列北部引发火灾；以色列国防军用炮火攻击发射场</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 03:20:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-live/25-gazans-reported-dead-in-rafah-strike-idf-first-probe-does-not-indicate-strike-there/00000190-3dea-d8cb-a19d-7debec640005</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡前雇员因欺凌、侵犯权利而获得 24 万美元赔偿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/former-netanyahu-employees-to-receive-240-000-for-bullying-rights-violations/00000190-3b89-da42-a1ba-7feb2c6e0000</link><description>两名维修工感觉自己像“现代奴隶”，其中一名经常违反程序被派往该家庭的私人住宅清洁游泳池。一名在该住所工作的厨师声称没有获得加班费</description><pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 03:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article/.premium/former-netanyahu-employees-to-receive-240-000-for-bullying-rights-violations/00000190-3b89-da42-a1ba-7feb2c6e0000</guid></item><item><title>去年，我决定放弃我的犹太身份。事情没有按计划进行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/last-year-i-decided-to-turn-my-back-on-my-jewish-identity-it-didnt-go-as-planned/00000190-3ccf-da42-a1ba-7fefec8a0000</link><description>我对内塔尼亚胡-本-格维尔政府成立的最初反应是冷落我的犹太教，但我的尝试失败了——就像许多试图逃避民族身份但失败的人一样</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 22:23:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-22/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/last-year-i-decided-to-turn-my-back-on-my-jewish-identity-it-didnt-go-as-planned/00000190-3ccf-da42-a1ba-7fefec8a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的切尔克斯小社区在炮火中仍保留其烹饪传统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-06-22/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-tiny-circassian-community-maintains-its-culinary-traditions-under-fire/00000190-3c99-d91c-abba-ff9980cf0000</link><description>在以色列北部的卡夫卡马，餐馆提供以传统切尔克斯奶酪为基础的美味佳肴。在其姊妹村雷哈尼亚 (Rehaniya)，美食旅游业因战争而被摧毁，当地企业正在艰难生存</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 21:58:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-06-22/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-tiny-circassian-community-maintains-its-culinary-traditions-under-fire/00000190-3c99-d91c-abba-ff9980cf0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日：两次比较——以及一个已实现的预测</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/october-7-two-comparisons-and-a-forecast-that-was-realized/00000190-3c45-d8cb-a19d-7d47bcde0000</link><description>与每一个历史事件一样，八个多月前的哈马斯大屠杀是独一无二的，但它可以分为不同的层次，可以与类似事件进行比较，从而加深我们对它的理解</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 20:58:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/october-7-two-comparisons-and-a-forecast-that-was-realized/00000190-3c45-d8cb-a19d-7d47bcde0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-巴勒斯坦和平可能与我们想象的完全不同</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israeli-palestinian-peace-may-look-entirely-different-from-how-we-imagine-it/00000190-3c3a-d16c-a7b0-7ebf4ae40000</link><description>各国人民之间的和平不一定是爱情故事，也可以建立在利益联盟的基础上。由于“和平变革”的进程，有些地方已经发挥了作用</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:51:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israeli-palestinian-peace-may-look-entirely-different-from-how-we-imagine-it/00000190-3c3a-d16c-a7b0-7ebf4ae40000</guid></item><item><title>作为美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 的战地记者，阿尔瓦·达蒙 (Arwa Damon) 认为她已经看到了一切。然后她去了加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/as-a-cnn-war-reporter-arwa-damon-thought-she-had-seen-everything-then-she-went-to-gaza/00000190-3bdd-d768-adf8-3fff8a400000</link><description>叙利亚内战期间，她通过下水道进入霍姆斯，后来亲眼目睹了伊斯兰国在摩苏尔制造的恐怖。作为美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 的高级记者，阿尔瓦·达蒙 (Arwa Damon) 报道了中东最严重的战区。但没有一个地方比加沙更可怕，她作为人道主义组织负责人访问了加沙：“我看到了人类灵魂的死亡”</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/as-a-cnn-war-reporter-arwa-damon-thought-she-had-seen-everything-then-she-went-to-gaza/00000190-3bdd-d768-adf8-3fff8a400000</guid></item><item><title>纽约时报：以色列的斯莫特里奇记录了加强对约旦河西岸控制的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/nyt-israels-smotrich-recorded-describing-plan-to-increase-control-over-west-bank/00000190-3c0d-d768-adf8-3cbf01e40000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇讨论的计划将赋予国防部内为他工作的文职人员而不是军队在被占领土上更多的权力，该计划已在过去 18 个月内逐步实施</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:14:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/nyt-israels-smotrich-recorded-describing-plan-to-increase-control-over-west-bank/00000190-3c0d-d768-adf8-3cbf01e40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方以暴力、错误逮捕和监视镇压抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-police-crack-down-on-protesters-with-violence-false-arrests-and-surveillance/00000190-3a6a-dea6-add5-faea16460000</link><description>六月标志着警察和示威者之间关系的转折点，民意调查显示，许多以色列人害怕参加因暴力事件不断升级而举行的抗议活动</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 17:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-police-crack-down-on-protesters-with-violence-false-arrests-and-surveillance/00000190-3a6a-dea6-add5-faea16460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 259 天：以色列军队加大对加沙地带的攻击力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-259-israeli-army-steps-up-attacks-across-the-gaza-strip/00000190-3bba-d49b-a1bd-7bfbdb960000</link><description>以色列国防军袭击加沙全境 ■ 人质之母：不会让内塔尼亚胡“背着人质玩小政治” ■ 美国国务院：就内塔尼亚胡视频反复讨论不会“有成效” ■ 亚美尼亚承认巴勒斯坦国■ 战争进入 259 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 17:11:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-259-israeli-army-steps-up-attacks-across-the-gaza-strip/00000190-3bba-d49b-a1bd-7bfbdb960000</guid></item><item><title>无人机没有铁穹：以色列国防军寻求应对真主党日益严重的威胁的答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/no-iron-dome-for-drones-idf-seeks-answers-to-growing-hezbollah-threat/00000190-3b38-d49b-a1bd-7b79f46b0000</link><description>真主党成功地挑战了以色列的防空系统，部分原因在于它在叙利亚内战中获得的经验。当以色列军队寻求新的防御方法时，武装直升机已被证明出奇的有效</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 17:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/no-iron-dome-for-drones-idf-seeks-answers-to-growing-hezbollah-threat/00000190-3b38-d49b-a1bd-7b79f46b0000</guid></item><item><title>21 岁巴勒斯坦人被控四月在约旦河西岸谋杀以色列青少年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/21-year-old-palestinian-charged-with-murder-of-israeli-teen-in-west-bank-in-april/00000190-3a98-da42-a1ba-7ffa08ad0000</link><description>起诉书称，艾哈迈德·达瓦布沙一年前对伊斯兰国产生了兴趣，并认为每个非穆斯林都是异教徒。军法署署长表示，在杀害 14 岁犹太牧羊人本雅明·阿希米尔后，达瓦布沙寻找更多受害者</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 16:08:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/21-year-old-palestinian-charged-with-murder-of-israeli-teen-in-west-bank-in-april/00000190-3a98-da42-a1ba-7ffa08ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以军加速拉法突击 坦克向北和西推进</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-accelerates-rafah-assaults-tanks-advancing-northward-and-westward/00000190-3ac5-d768-adf8-3ef74df50000</link><description>加沙地带南部城市的居民报告说，过去两天，以色列国防军从海上和空中发动袭击时，不断发生爆炸和枪击事件。拉法市长：由于轰炸，“人们正在帐篷里死去”</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:58:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-accelerates-rafah-assaults-tanks-advancing-northward-and-westward/00000190-3ac5-d768-adf8-3ef74df50000</guid></item><item><title>亚美尼亚宣布承认巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/armenia-announces-recognition-of-palestinian-state/00000190-39e3-d768-adf8-3df3ea000000</link><description>该国外交部称，加沙地带持续的战争和严峻的人道主义局势是其做出这一决定的原因。以色列召见亚美尼亚大使予以谴责</description><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 12:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-21/ty-article/.premium/armenia-announces-recognition-of-palestinian-state/00000190-39e3-d768-adf8-3df3ea000000</guid></item></channel></rss>